      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[15]/10/78 ¶ Theday in the dateis missing. The letter was registered at the Chief Secretary's Department on 16 October 1878; it is dated on the assumption that the letter was written the day before it...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">78.10.15<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Odgers</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">O78/11279, unit 1069, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>[15]/10/78<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">The</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>day in the date</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is missing</seg>. The letter was registered at the Chief Secretary's Department on 16 October 1878; i<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">t is dated on the assumption that the letter was written the day before it was registered.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I write a few lines, dear Mr Odgers, to ask whether you will kindly remind the hon. Graham Berry of my great wish for obtaining the £1800 for buildings, on the estimates before the parliamentary session closes, as otherwise a year will be lost.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You remember perhaps, that £900 lapsed two years ago. I am so very<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">eager</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to get at last the Office-Museum and Laboratory Branches again in superior working order, and to provide space for the constantly increasing collections &amp; working material. The present only room is so much out of repair, that it will be best to build anew in Albert-Park I ask for no horticultural votes. Advise me kindly, whether I ought again to submit two official applications, one to the C.S., the other to the Minister of public works.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. MacPherson, 16 April 1877<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">(in this edition as 77-04-16a)</seg>, M to W. Odgers, 21 June 1877, and M to W. Odgers,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">23 July 1878.</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">A note on the file refers to the last of these.</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; "
                        xml:lang="en">A bit cryptic: what does it say?<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>That letter has an annotation<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>interpreting it as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a "promise" to move forward in 1878 having<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>been made!</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
